; BIND zone snippet for Cloudflare DNS import (GitHub Pages)
; Dashboard: hackerplanet.dev -> DNS -> Records -> Import and Export -> Import
; After import: click each A/CNAME record -> turn OFF proxy (grey cloud / DNS only)

$ORIGIN hackerplanet.dev.
@       300     IN      A       185.199.108.153
@       300     IN      A       185.199.109.153
@       300     IN      A       185.199.110.153
@       300     IN      A       185.199.111.153
www     300     IN      CNAME   salvador-Data.github.io.
